      "instruction": "Add the curry powder and continue to saut\u00e9 with the onion mixture for one minute more. Add about 1/4 cup of water to the skillet along with the fresh spinach and continue to saut\u00e9 until the spinach has wilted. The water will help steam and wilt the spinach (no water needed if using frozen spinach)."
    },
